orities are preparing for.\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2800, \"end\": 2806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.698739914932469e-20, \"text\": \"Hecker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a security analyst\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Institute\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"International Relations\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"the various threats\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is a huge event attracting millions of people.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge event\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 2999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The main threat for the French authorities is terrorism, specifically the jihadist threat.\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3025, \"end\": 3031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5508519141507472, \"rank\": 0.7129793321850184, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The main threat\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"terrorism\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3056}, {\"ngram\": \"specifically the jihadist threat\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there are also concerns about far-right activists and non-violent disruptors.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"far-right activists\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"non-violent disruptors\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the cyber threat is significant, but the authorities are well-prepared to counter it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cyber threat\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To maximize protection and minimize risks, French authorities have mobilised 45,000 police officers andgendarmes, over 10,000 soldiers, and 20,000 private security officers.\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3324, \"end\": 3330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5508519141507472, \"rank\": 0.7129793321850184, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"protection and minimize risks\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"45,000 police officers\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"20,000 private security officers\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to a request from French authorities, 42 Garda\\u00ed from Ireland will assist in policing Paris from July 25 to August 12, with a further 12 Garda\\u00ed for the Paralympics from August 27 to September 9.\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3485, \"end\": 3491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5508519141507472, \"rank\": 0.7129793321850184, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3520, \"end\": 3527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999122338, \"r